name: Hope Tee
description:
This shirt is one of the first designs from lessthenthree. It is 50% cotton and 50% polyester; this reduces shrinkage and allows the shirt to keep its original shape. The retail price is 15.00 but the unit price online is 17.50 because of shipping and handling. When checking out with paypal please note where you live, etc and any additional comments. 

** There are large sizes, so if you want a large put a small in the oprtion but state in paypal that you want a large.**
